    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK464">
<l>teḷivi lataṉait toṭaṅkā riḷiveṉṉu</l>
<l> mētappā ṭañcu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who fear reproach will not commence anything which has not been (thoroughly considered) and made clear to them.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
